---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import { BRAND } from "../lib/brand";
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<Base
  title={`Terms of service | ${BRAND.name}`}
  description="The terms and conditions under which we do business."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5 md:px-8 py-16">
    <nav class="text-xs text-bone/40 mb-4">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-rust">Home</a> <span class="mx-2">/</span> <span>Terms</span>
    </nav>
    <h1 class="font-display text-5xl">Terms of service</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-bone/50">Last updated 20 April {year}.</p>
    <div class="mt-10 space-y-5 text-bone/80 leading-relaxed">
      <p>These terms govern your use of harmonythreads.co (the "Site"), operated by {BRAND.name} ({BRAND.address.street}, {BRAND.address.city}, {BRAND.address.postcode}, {BRAND.address.country}).</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-8">Orders & pricing</h2>
      <p>All prices are in GBP and inclusive of VAT. We reserve the right to refuse or cancel an order if a price has been listed in error. Digital products are licensed for personal use and are non-refundable once downloaded.</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-8">Shipping & returns</h2>
      <p>See our <a href="/shipping" class="underline hover:text-rust">shipping & returns page</a> for the detail. In brief: 30 days to return unworn apparel and sealed fragrance, no returns on opened fragrance or downloaded digital goods.</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-8">Intellectual property</h2>
      <p>All graphics, photographs, and written content are © {year} {BRAND.name}. The rights to the musical names and references on our graphic apparel remain with their respective rights-holders; our designs are tributes, not endorsements.</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-8">Liability</h2>
      <p>Nothing in these terms limits our liability for death or personal injury caused by negligence. Otherwise, our liability is limited to the value of the order in question.</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-8">Governing law</h2>
      <p>These terms are governed by English law. Disputes are subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the English courts.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
